The use of #P-completeness and #SAT-hardness also suggests that the paper may belong to the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) sub-category. The mention of independent sets and minimal separators suggests that the paper may belong to the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) sub-category. Finally, the focus on locally-optimal structures suggests that the paper may also belong to the cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) sub-category.
